    "updated_at": "2016-12-21T14:42:20Z",
    "body": "The error message clearly tells you that the `node` executable is not found in any of the directories listed in your `PATH` environment variable. You need to ensure `/usr/local/bin` is added to `PATH`, and addition you need to ensure the spawned child process is seeing the \"correct\" `PATH` variable as well. \r\n\r\nTo check whether `node` is discoverable at the user/system level, run e.g. `which node` in a terminal."
  },
