    "created_at": "2016-12-21T21:28:17Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-12-21T21:28:17Z",
    "body": "> Is it possible to spawn a CLI electron instance (No window) in an Electron app ?\r\n\r\nYes, you have to set the `ELECTRON_RUN_AS_NODE` environment variable though.\r\n\r\nhttp://electron.atom.io/docs/api/environment-variables/#electronrunasnode\r\n\r\nYou also want to call spawn with the path of `process.execPath`.\r\n"
  },
